{"tid":303541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英向全體公務員發信　感謝各人過去5年盡職盡責","createTime":"2017-06-30T09:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T09:53:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"872ffe81519e24387c5c478a080901d5740bb207","tid":303541,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1339223_1_20170630165010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1339223_1_20170630165010.jpg&h=4f5ec786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官梁振英在任期最後1天，代表問責團隊向全體政府及公務員發信件，表示感謝各人在過去5年緊守崗位，盡職盡責，為香港的社會和經濟發展，為改善市民生活的辛勤付出。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又說，對香港的未來充滿信心，並希望全體同事同心同德，支持和配合新一屆特區政府施政，為香港作出新的貢獻。"},{"pid":"0dad34d72996026dc0482f431bd715ec1b68730e","tid":303541,"uid":53568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"快撚D過主啦柒頭"},{"pid":"da7ff42529c0e5512ec8dafffd220cf2a0fdcfcd","tid":303541,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e66b8d514df27df1f4513dbc06f9976dd31580","tid":303541,"uid":33787,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fd728ca886526c235e9388601db16f82fb073e6","tid":303541,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"8700"},{"pid":"3313733620149ea5a65919c905ae67d740b73166","tid":303541,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:38:01.000Z","msg":"走喇仆街"},{"pid":"22de15ee51a2c6df4f09578d0309de83f74e8b43","tid":303541,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"跟撚左幾多佢d 手尾"},{"pid":"1a2a257222d3c8bcac9e228dd197ed678dd76676","tid":303541,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":